---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About Us"
  description="Learn more about Calyan Studio, our mission, and our team."
>
  <main
    class="px-4 md:px-8 lg:px-16 py-8 md:py-12 lg:py-16 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto"
  >
    <section class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-[#343a40]">Our History</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#343a40] max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Calyan Studio began with a simple idea: to bridge the gap between innovative concepts and their digital realization. Founded in [Year of Founding] by a group of passionate technologists and creative minds, we started as a small team with a big dream. Our early days were marked by relentless learning, experimentation, and a deep commitment to solving complex challenges for our first clients.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#343a40] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Over the years, we've grown, evolved, and expanded our expertise, but our core values have remained constant. We've embraced new technologies, adapted to changing market demands, and consistently pushed the boundaries of what's possible in the digital realm. Today, Calyan Studio stands as a testament to perseverance, creativity, and the power of a dedicated team working towards a common goal.
      </p>
    </section>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-[#343a40]">
        About Calyan Studio
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-[#6c757d] max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We are a creative studio dedicated to transforming ideas into
        exceptional digital experiences. Discover our journey, values, and the
        passionate team behind our success.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-20 items-center">
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl"
      >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#007bff]">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#343a40] mb-4">
          At Calyan Studio, our mission is to empower businesses and individuals with cutting-edge digital solutions that not only meet but exceed their expectations. We are dedicated to crafting impactful and user-centric experiences that drive significant growth, foster innovation, and create lasting value.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#343a40]">
          We believe in the transformative power of technology to turn ambitious ideas into tangible realities. Our commitment lies in delivering excellence in every project we undertake, ensuring that each solution is robust, scalable, and perfectly aligned with our clients' strategic goals.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div
        class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl"
      >
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-[#007bff]">Our Vision</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#343a40] mb-4">
          Our vision is to be a globally recognized leader in digital solutions, celebrated for our unparalleled creativity, exceptional technical prowess, and unwavering dedication to client success. We envision a future where technology is a seamless extension of human potential, simplifying complexities and opening new avenues for progress.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-[#343a40]">
          We are committed to building enduring partnerships based on mutual trust, transparent collaboration, and a shared passion for continuous learning and improvement. Through our work, we aspire to inspire, innovate, and leave a lasting positive impact on the digital landscape.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-[#343a40]">Our Core Values</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md"
        >
          <i class="fas fa-lightbulb text-5xl text-[#007bff] mb-4"></i>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-[#343a40]">Innovation</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6c757d]">
            Constantly exploring new technologies and creative approaches to
            deliver unique solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md"
        >
          <i class="fas fa-handshake text-5xl text-[#007bff] mb-4"></i>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-[#343a40]">Collaboration</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6c757d]">
            Working closely with clients and within our team to achieve shared
            goals and foster mutual growth.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md"
        >
          <i class="fas fa-award text-5xl text-[#007bff] mb-4"></i>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2 text-[#343a40]">Excellence</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6c757d]">
            Committed to delivering robust, reliable, and high-performing
            solutions that exceed expectations.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-[#343a40]">
        Meet Our Talented Team
      </h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl"
        >
          <img
            src="/team/gaurav87565.jpg"
            alt="Gaurav Uchil"
            class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 border-4 border-[#007bff] object-cover"
          />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#343a40]">Gaurav Uchil</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6c757d]">CEO (Chief Executive Officer)</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-4">
            <button
              data-url="http://github.com/gaurav87565"
              class="text-[#181717] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
            </button>
            <button
              data-url="https://x.com/gaurav87565"
              class="text-[#000000] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
            </button>
            <button
              data-url="https://gaurav.dapirates.xyz/"
              class="text-[#007bff] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl"
        >
          <img
            src="/team/gtmsudarshan.jpg"
            alt="Sudarshan Gautam"
            class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 border-4 border-[#007bff] object-cover"
          />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#343a40]">Sudarshan Gautam</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6c757d]">CTO (Chief Technology Officer)</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-4">
            <button
              data-url="https://www.facebook.com/realsudarshan"
              class="text-[#1877F2] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
            </button>
            <button
              data-url="https://github.com/GTMSudarshan"
              class="text-[#181717] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
            </button>
            <button
              data-url="https://portfolio.gtmsudarshan.com.np/"
              class="text-[#007bff] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl"
        >
          <img
            src="/team/kiratdewas.jpg"
            alt="Biraj Rai"
            class="w-32 h-32 rounded-full mx-auto mb-4 border-4 border-[#007bff] object-cover"
          />
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#343a40]">Biraj Rai</h3>
          <p class="text-[#6c757d]">Berozgaar (Unemployed)</p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-4">
            <button
              data-url="https://www.facebook.com/neppixel"
              class="text-[#1877F2] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
            </button>
            <button
              data-url="https://github.com/birajrai"
              class="text-[#181717] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
            </button>
            <button
              data-url="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kiratdewas/"
              class="text-[#0A66C2] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
            </button>
            <button
              data-url="https://biraj.is-a.dev/"
              class="text-[#007bff] text-2xl focus:outline-none"
            >
              <i class="fas fa-globe"></i>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="text-center mb-20">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-12 text-[#343a40]">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#343a40] max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Have a project in mind or just want to say hello? We'd love to hear from you! Reach out to us through the following channels:
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-8">
        <a href="mailto:info@calyanstudio.com" class="text-[#007bff] text-2xl focus:outline-none">
          <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
          <span class="block text-base mt-2">Email Us</span>
        </a>
        <a href="tel:+1234567890" class="text-[#28a745] text-2xl focus:outline-none">
          <i class="fas fa-phone"></i>
          <span class="block text-base mt-2">Call Us</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-[#6f42c1] text-2xl focus:outline-none">
          <i class="fas fa-file-alt"></i>
          <span class="block text-base mt-2">Contact Form</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
    const socialButtons = document.querySelectorAll("button[data-url]");
    socialButtons.forEach((button) => {
      button.addEventListener("click", () => {
        const url = (button as HTMLElement).dataset.url;
        if (url) {
          window.open(url, "_blank");
        }
      });
    });
  });
</script>
